name: Sugar Cane - Black Gloss Frame - Neutral Grey Polarized Lens

features: Lens: Neutral Grey - Offers the highest available light reduction for the richest colours and sharpest contrast.

Bridge: Saddle-style fixed bridge with embedded non-slip silicone nose pads.
Finishing Treatment: Four color options available in a gloss finish.
